name: Moments of Chance – MOC-12
description:
Every Moment draws their pixels from a single well known artwork, created in the last 1500 years. 

Seed artwork is chosen at random at time of creation, but this artwork is not forgotten – just lost.

Each moment in the life of the work is unique. Blink and that moment is lost forever.

Moments of Chance: Drop 1
Created by Jonny Scholes, 2021.
